{
  "stem": "13313.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Whatever little food we had, three days no food, three days no leaving the room, this kind of stuff.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So it was the day of the egg.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that was her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So beatings would be almost like daily.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Though-- we did very hard work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We cut the wood in the wood shed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We had to-- we looked after the vegetable garden.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We had to carry this basket with all the clothes to Boechout, which was another village.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We went to church in Edegem.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We lived in Hove.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And went to school for a while in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we went to the laundry in Boechout.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And all these are two, three kilometers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So my brother and I used to drag this heavy basket with laundry.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Had to stop every-- we were very weak, so every 10, 15 minutes, we had to stop because we just couldn't carry it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "On the way, naturally, there was the odd cherry tree, apple tree, there was a season.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So we used to stop and-- and-- and feed ourselves.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was that kind of work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Practically no food, no drink, and be beating almost every day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was our life.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And what if-- if you asked why or if you protested?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was out  of the question.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- for-- for not doing anything wrong or inadvertently making-- slipping up once in a while we got treated like that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Any-- any-- any question would've been an act of-- I don't recall even, it wasn't even an option to-- to-- to ask anything.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was ironic that I would have to say that during World War II, between the people-- between the first two years and the years in hiding, you know, we circulated as their children.",
      "word_count": 34
    }
  ],
